Thus it has indirectly confirmed that the current operators in the Czech Republic are not very much in favour of this idea.
Rather, they try to do everything because you do not create any potential competitor.
For some time now he has not hidden his interest in starting a virtual operator, the GTS Novera group that would like to take another step to become a real competitor of Telefónica O2 in the field of corporate customers.
“We have a great interest in being able to offer our customers not only fixed services but also mobile telecommunications.
