So maybe better times will come.
Informal information suggests that the first virtual operator should be available by the end of the year.
For now, however, an impenetrable wall of silence is erected around his creation.
“At the moment, we do not believe that there is room in the Czech market for the creation of a full-fledged virtual operator.
