T-Mobil press spokeswoman Martina Kemrová adds in a rare agreement with the O2 statement: “We have not noticed any vital and beneficial commercial project for both of us, on which it is possible to continue to build.”
“In the T-Mobil network, a virtual operator will hardly appear by the end of the year.
