The numerous initiatives promoted in the school field for a more direct awareness on the part of young people facing the world of work are of particular importance.
It is necessary to keep the attention to the phenomenon alive, not to slow down in the alarm about its social gravity, to apply and improve the legislative rules.
For his part, the President of the House Gianfranco Fini stressed "how the phenomenon of white deaths constitutes an absolute social emergency, which offends the conscience of each of us and imposes on all institutions a determined commitment aimed at putting an urgent end to it".
